---
import CaseStudy from '../../layouts/CaseStudy.astro';
---

<CaseStudy
  title="SPRAYCATION — CWK. Work"
  description="How CWK. built the brand foundation and operational backbone of the SPRAYCATION Mural Tour while the campaign was already in motion across 6 cities."
  category="Experiential Campaign"
  client="SPRAYCATION"
  headline="Building an Experiential Campaign While in Motion"
  duration="Jan–Nov 2025"
  result="6 cities"
  resultLabel="Tour executed"
>

  <!-- Stats row -->
  <div class="cs-stats">
    <div class="cs-stat">
      <span class="cs-stat-num">6 cities</span>
      <span class="cs-stat-label">Tour</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cs-stat">
      <span class="cs-stat-num">11 months</span>
      <span class="cs-stat-label">Live build</span>
    </div>
    <div class="cs-stat">
      <span class="cs-stat-num">2026</span>
      <span class="cs-stat-label">Scale ready</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <div class="cs-section">
    <h2>SPRAYCATION</h2>
    <p>
      SPRAYCATION is a female-led experiential art movement built around large-scale public murals, storytelling, and creative action.
    </p>
    <p>
      The tour for 2025 centered on a single message: <strong>You Are Magic</strong> — a call to reclaim creative power, occupy public space, and choose yourself.
    </p>
    <p>
      CWK. began working with Zuzu in January 2025. The tour launched in June and ran through November.
    </p>
    <div class="yt-embed">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/indEyPSLvlI?rel=0"
        title="SPRAYCATION Mural Tour 2025 Kick-off"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
        loading="lazy"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- The Work -->
  <div class="cs-section">
    <h2>The Work</h2>
    <p>
      CWK.'s role was to build the brand foundation and operational backbone while the tour was already in motion.
    </p>
    <p>That included:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Centering the entire tour around a single narrative</li>
      <li>Hiring and coordinating an operations team in real time</li>
      <li>Creating backend systems for sales, customer service, and partners</li>
      <li>Designing repeatable processes and templates</li>
      <li>Supporting Zuzu in the mural reveal / celebration events in select cities</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Everything was built under live conditions.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- The Result -->
  <div class="cs-section">
    <h2>The Result</h2>
    <p>
      SPRAYCATION moved from an ambitious art idea to a repeatable, fundable experiential brand.
    </p>
    <p>The tour proved:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The message holds across cities</li>
      <li>The model works beyond one-off murals</li>
      <li>The experience can be packaged, sold, and scaled</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      2024 proved the concept.<br />
      2025 refined the narrative.<br />
      2026 is built for scale.
    </p>
    <p>
      Follow Zuzu's work on <a href="https://www.instagram.com/zuzubee/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

</CaseStudy>
